item.title: Prayer bpn10244 in Māori
item.description: ##KARAKIA MŌ TE AKO MAI I NGĀ PAPATUHI O TE KAUPAPA TAPU ##HE MEA WHAKAATU KI NGĀ BAHÁ’Í O AMERIKA ME KĀNATA E Koe Te Atua Kotahi Tonu! e Koe Te Ariki o te Kīngitanga! Ko ēnei wairua ora Tāu tauā o te rangi. Āwhinatia mai rātou, ā, meinga rātou kia wikitōria tahi me ngā tauā o te Huinga o Runga Rawa, kia rite ai rātou ki te hokowhitu-ā-Tū ka toa ai ki runga o ngā whenua mā te aroha o Te Atua me te mārama o ngā whakaakoranga tapu.

item.title: Prayer bpn10245 in Māori
item.description: ##MEA WHAKAATU KI NGĀ BAHÁ’Í O TE TONGA O AMERIKA *Ia wairua e haereere nei mā ngā taonenui, ngā taoneiti, me ngā kāinga o ēnei Kotahitanga, ā, kei roto o te horahanga o te kakara o Te Atua, māna tēnei whakatātakitanga e titiro ia ata. E tōku Atua! e tōku Atua! Kei te kite Koe i tōku whakaiti me te ngoikoretanga, e warea rawa atu ana ki te mahi nui whakahara, e pūmau ana ki te whakaara i Tāu kupu ki waenga o Āu iwi.
